text.headline:
Whitney Houston
1963 - 2012
text.text: Houston's voice caught the imagination of the world propelling her to superstardom at an early age becoming one of the most awarded performers of our time. This is a look into the amazing heights she achieved and her personal struggles with substance abuse and a tumultuous marriage.

text.headline: Inside Solana Colosseum Hackathon | Interview with Co-Founder Matty Tay

text.headline: London BuildStop Recap | 19 Jan 2024 | SuperteamUK
text.text:
SuperteamUK members can now join us Every Friday at our co-working space for web3 builders, leaders and creatives in London (Every Friday: 10M - 9PM)! 🇬🇧

​​BuildStop Highlights:

- 60+ premium desk spaces
- Workshops on Solana, DeFi, NFTs, and more
- Project work, team building, and networking
- Expert support, open mics, and demo days
- Comfortable venue with WiFi, workstations, free drinks & snacks
- Exclusive events, including City Hall every Friday at 7PM
- Receive your 'Day Pass' wristband on arrival. Return it, or incur a replacement fee. 🤝

Connect with developers & builders, and gain insights from industry leaders. Open Monday to Friday for talks, workshops, and a demo day.

For more info, join us on the SuperteamUK Discord. Don't miss London's web3 community in action! 

#SuperteamUK #Web3London  #Solana #

text.headline: H from Moongate on London Buildstation | Superteam UK | Solana
text.text:
We are delighted to have H with us, a superteam UK member, and co-founder of Moongate. 
Moongate allows Solana Dapps to onboard Ethereum users on Solana effortlessly!

H has not only been a Superteam UK member but has also been a buildstation maxi, who often shows up to the door before organisers in the morning!

Kudos to his grind and listen to his thoughts on how buildstation is a game-changer for him and his Hyperdrive submission!

#SuperteamUK #Solana #DeFi #Moongate #Superteam #Coworking #Huckletree #London

text.headline: Unveiling the Members Only Superteam UK Merch Boxes ft. Uzy1000x from Mob Studios
Caleb from Big Brain Holdings | London Buildstation | Superteam UK | Solana
text.text:
Its week 2 at London Buildstation from Superteam UK, builders from across the country have come down to learn, earn, build and chill for two weeks under one roof!

During the course of London Web3 week and Buildstation, we had several OGs and veterans from the crypto industry come down to the venue and give valuable insights and conduct workshops on various areas of crypto.

Caleb, investor at Big Brain Holdings also joined us for a workshop on "Steps to complete your first seed raise" on Monday, 9th September following a massively successful session by Veets the previous week,  analyst at Big Brain Holdings.


Watch this video to learn more about Caleb's thoughts about building in the UK, networking during events and more!
